Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与被称为悼词朗诵者的火雾战士的激烈战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜得到了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利然后分别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但当时的我却没能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜新的战斗快要逼近城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别追银了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个光追是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微留情点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己提出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的  肯定不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热  真的好热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一大早就这么热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天热是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你现在懒得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算坚持每天早上的锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全没有进步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该考虑才能的成分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  已经留好退路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想说的是  现阶段里  别用这种话来逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说起才能的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在能更好行动的基础上才谈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了  池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了  池同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池  你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  因为父亲工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到大量御崎水上乐园的门票
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就发给班上的同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上乐园就是那个最近才开张的「啊哈」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天啊  泳衣啊  御崎水上乐园  啊哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我想大家会不会很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  平井同学也有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  泳衣打算怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一副懒懒的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得拿到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明后天就
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上课之前  对老师就有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领带太花哨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很新潮啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛  悠二那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着一张票傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游乐设施的入场券吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类很喜欢玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说来也很合乎情理了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样  心情和脸都太懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才没进步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  亚拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水上乐园是不是和浴室一样很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  去屋顶吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜还是没在中午前回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  平井同学去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邻镇的面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？为什么又
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  可能中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然蜜瓜包重要的就是这种既香脆又松软的口感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  不介意的话大家一起吃便当好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人在一起边吃边开心地聊天比较有滋味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  便当总是吃便利店的饭团呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛  老妈说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子如果一日三餐都吃母亲亲手做的饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能出人投地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.10,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的话不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是邀请坂井去水上乐园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  有事想商量下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得池同学的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天大家一起去水上乐园如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学  大家是指
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  全班的话好像太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的人和那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边两人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学也没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班级里的女主角不来的话就不能开始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期天10点在水上乐园集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样  你们可别迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩从以前开始就老是迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方  抱歉啊  有些事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像做了对不起绪方的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说周末无论如何都要把玛裘莉小姐  带到外面去的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐天天在房子里喝的烂醉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再不带她去哪玩玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体就会坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这窝囊的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我烂醉的睡美人——玛裘莉·顿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  早上好  欢迎回来  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件泳衣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  也不那么花哨  这种挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪  绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都和男孩子一起去游泳池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛穿老土的泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试穿这个之前衣服就交我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.18,0:10:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱情爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  快穿快穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再  再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就快让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方同学  你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是穿这个看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了普通的一件头就行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  小夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泳衣给你买来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和大家一起去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还穿学校的泳衣也太那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太那个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说能穿上在学校不能穿的  可爱泳衣的意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就试穿看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里好好等着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不知道学习这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了是误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近有这个的话夏天可算是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中和佐藤好像真的不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话也一直没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们5个开心的玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侣骑马战？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男女一组进行水中骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜组的奖品是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐厅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豪华晚餐免费招待券和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手制面包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手制面包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你的眼眸干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干  干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正下午才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然少个男士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个等下再考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要着急不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是缘和一美的泳衣时装秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是平井小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是吉田小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪  绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  别管那么多  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不偶尔外出的话身体可会坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的情况出门反而对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是这样也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,荣太  那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛裘莉小姐  真的要现在进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够避暑的只有这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不如改明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的日子有些不合适
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词朗诵者来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？悼词的？那个人来这了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然感觉不到杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到两个火雾战士都来这个游泳池悠闲地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有点想笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去下小卖部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐一说出口就不听别人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一碰到绪方她们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该说什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.58,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能那么容易就碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你们俩在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是叫他们去买个酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启作和荣太都不知道在搞什么飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈  对你粗暴的喝酒方式终于忍受不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝了我的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道  虽然不太清楚  大概是三角关系之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  果然只是来玩的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可没心情和你干架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想打的话找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水边喝点酒再睡一觉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词朗诵者也就满足咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼词朗诵者作为火雾战士也到头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但对我们来说无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  昨天说不去是为了吓大家一跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想简单地说去太无趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是在这里突然出现热闹一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  田中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我也不告诉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话会参加骑马战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.60,0:17:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑马战？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带子连着的两人就组队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多出来的人就专心加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  大姐可是一直在等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起玛裘莉小姐的事曝光来得要好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我放手咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎水上乐园特产
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水中情侣骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢到最多头巾的队伍就是优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  头巾被夺走或是两人分开就为失败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池那家伙跑哪去上厕所了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说会好好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在规定时间内抢到最多头巾的情侣将会得到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看得到夜景的餐厅的晚餐和豪华奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同学在能看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和坂井同学在能看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了的话蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了的话蜜瓜包任吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗  田中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是靠你的机动力了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么紧张的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  热闹激烈的水中骑马战开幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限定时间为3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认识的互相争夺也不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抢别人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一美也挺不赖的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑马战果然还是要靠头脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也有不靠头脑都很厉害的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  还要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平井同学好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是佐藤比较厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用勉强和他们打了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间所剩无几了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下来的情侣也越来越少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  好不容易留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样等到时间结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能拿到点什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能像这样待在坂井同学身边就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔唷  平井组行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕  逃吧  吉田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打败我们也没意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是锻炼的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.42,0:20:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能那样的投机  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同学  再把身体俯低些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就  就算这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小缘  莫非是因为我和坂井同学粘在一起才发火的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再追近些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是极限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同学  来了  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二  觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜者是捡到便宜的冈田组
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来冈田老师也来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但  这也算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是他太太吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  干嘛要追上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且夏娜也总是总是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年  你也喝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年不能喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真头疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道大家怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  真抱歉把你丢一边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像把奇怪的东西当枕头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脖子好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就在这里解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期一学校再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为什么要追来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.06,0:24:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用语言表达的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.46,0:24:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜独自一人挥舞着剑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.20,0:24:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥漫着磷子的惨叫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后城市里出现了新的红世之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  纠缠的思念
